"const *` without an explicit type cast. In C, the functions only support "
"arguments of type :c:expr:`char * const *`. This can be overridden with the :"
"c:macro:`PY_CXX_CONST` macro. (Contributed by Serhiy Storchaka in :gh:"
"`65210`.)"
